{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:0","text":"在六个光谱波段上计算薄膜干涉效果。"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:1","text":"Input Parameters"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:2","text":"Input Color"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:3","text":"会被干涉效果扰动的颜色。"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:4","text":"Eta"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:5","text":"薄膜的折射率。这里假定外部介质为空气。"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:6","text":"Spread"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:7","text":"折射率在整个色谱上的变化幅度。"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:8","text":"Thickness"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:9","text":"薄膜厚度，单位为纳米。"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:10","text":"Thickness Scale"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:11","text":"在此连接一个 pattern 来调制 thickness。它会乘以"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:12","text":"thickness"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:13","text":"值。"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:14","text":"Front Only"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:15","text":"仅在正面朝向点上计算干涉。默认情况下，两面都会计算。"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:16","text":"Output Parameters"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:17","text":"resultRGB"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:18","text":"颜色结果。"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:19","text":"resultR"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:20","text":"来自 resultRGB 输出的 R 通道。"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:21","text":"resultG"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:22","text":"来自 resultRGB 输出的 G 通道。"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:23","text":"resultB"}
{"item_id":"0fc1542da9:24","text":"来自 resultRGB 输出的 B 通道。"}
